{"tid":2457882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 鹽酥雞肉燥飯 配 麻辣青瓜","createTime":"2021-03-23T04:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T11:11:35.000Z","uid":33359,"like":24,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3551e05c22878c430416db3fca627c30df3d91b7","tid":2457882,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJRAF7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJRAF7u.jpg&h=c2c1b7a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjvNxec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjvNxec.jpg&h=b87247f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鹽酥雞炸得好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎返嚟嘅途中已經有啲淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係食落口都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉燥普普通通我都係鍾意一粒粒肉粒嗰隻魯肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青瓜幾新鮮爽脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個汁幾香辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個喉嚨都幾c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b10fdc344f54e415245d4f1d794a46a19d5588","tid":2457882,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90091bf957731ee76c711d31deee759a0278a1ca","tid":2457882,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a91f358762361523a88c3edc95f4e0aa6f7a09","tid":2457882,"uid":315852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"賣相好差<img s